Description:
Description:
In Opsporing Arrestanten in the Tab Goederen there is no functionality to copy goederen as in the remaining Goederen modules.

Currently when you add a Goed and save you have an additional button to copy.
This can be found in assistentie- rol/proces - enter for example bekende aangehouden verdachte or aangifte fill in mandatory fields and save.
A tab called Goederen will appear here you can see that you can Copy an entered goederen.
But when you go to Opsporing- arrestanten and tab goederen you cannot Copy the entered goed.

Solution:
Copy in Opsporing Arrestanten in the Tab Goederen the functionality to copy goederen as in the remaining Goederen modules.

Testplan:
Step 1: Go to Opsporing - Arrestanten - tab Goederen
Step 2: Open an existing Arrestenten record.
Step 3: Add in tab Goederen an object (goed) and Save.
Step 4: Go to this Goed and click on the copy button and save.
Step 5: it should be possible to copy this goed muultiple times and save.

Navigation:
Opsporing - Arrestanten - tab Goederen
